### Breakpoints:

- Mobile: 520px (0-520px is mobile)
- Tablet: 840px (521-840px is tablet)
- Desktop: 1200px (841-1200px is desktop)
- Large Desktop: 1440px (1201-1440px is large desktop)
- Limit container max-width to 1440px.